                            <div class="pb60" id="AlumniClub">
                                <div class="mainHd">Alumni Club</div>
                                <div class="textBox mb-20">The Alumni Club seeks to connect graduates with the
                                    university, maintain the continuity of the relationship and communication between
                                    graduates and the university, implement several activities for graduates, publish
                                    graduate news on the club's digital platforms, and prepare graduates to seize
                                    professional opportunities and participate effectively in the labor market by
                                    developing their technical and cognitive skills, and other important skills, such
                                    as: communication skills, management, problem solving, teamwork, interview
                                    preparation, and others.
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-30">
                                    <img src="/ust_website_alumni_club/static/src/images/alumni-club.jpg"
                                         alt="Alumni Club"/>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grayBg alumniLink">
                                    <span>University of Science and Technology Alumni Link</span>
                                    Check the university graduates via the link:
                                    <a href="#">Click here</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="pb60" id="StudentAchievements">
                                <div class="mainHd">Student Achievements</div>
                                <div class="textBox mb-20">
                                    <ul class="listText">
                                        <li>Students of the Faculty of Engineering at the University of Science and
                                            Technology participated in the competition organized by the Global Health
                                            Engineering Company, and won sixth place with their design of a low-cost
                                            current leakage testing device.
                                        </li>
                                        <li>The administration of the University of Science and Technology branch in
                                            Taiz, in coordination with the Student Affairs Department, honored the top
                                            students in the academic levels from various departments and scientific
                                            specializations in the branch for the academic year 2019-2020 AD.
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flexBox introBox itemCenter">
                                    <div class="left">
                                        <img src="/ust_website_alumni_club/static/src/images/community-services.jpg"
                                             alt="Community Services"/>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="right">
                                        <div class="mainHd">Community Services</div>
                                        <div class="textBox">Since its inception, the University of Science and
                                            Technology has paid great attention to providing service to the community in
                                            the field of public services and medical services related to various
                                            colleges and centers. Its participation in raising the level of community
                                            welfare, eradicating poverty, providing maternity care, and establishing
                                            scholarships for deserving students are among the few examples of its active
                                            participation in community affairs.
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="pb60" id="FutureVision">
                                <div class="mainHd">Future Vision</div>
                                <div class="textBox mb-30">Keen on the necessity of finding a means of communication
                                    between students and civil society institutions, and bridging the gap between
                                    university education and the labor market, the University of Science and Technology
                                    is always working to achieve career guidance for students; with the aim of
                                    developing the individual and collective skills of university students, and
                                    providing them with skills related to professional aspects, in addition to deepening
                                    their knowledge of themselves, increasing their confidence in their abilities, and
                                    training students professionally, and preparing them to enter the labor market, by
                                    holding courses and workshops that help them develop their skills, such as training
                                    them on how to prepare a CV, and how to deal correctly with job interviews.
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <img src="/ust_website_alumni_club/static/src/images/future-vision.jpg"
                                         alt="Future Vision"/>
                                </div>
